title: Carrie Underwood - Carnival Ride
description:
Carnival Ride is the second studio album from American country pop artist Carrie Underwood. It was released in the United States on October 23, 2007. It has recently been certified Double Platinum by the RIAA. The album includes the #1 country singles "So Small" and "All-American Girl". The album debuted at #1 on the US Billboard 200 Chart selling 527,000 copies, giving Underwood her first #1 album.
